description:
The Apostle Paul and Ezra explain that the Old Testament is really about a mystery concealing the person of Jesus.

Scripture
Isaiah 7, 53; Colossians 1:25-27

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: Ashley Wood, Brian Shoop

chapters.title: A MYSTERY Ezra & The Apostle Paul
